comments.body: Now that I've looked at the source code, I'm not sure this is the correct interface for Nightwatch Page Objects (https://github.com/nightwatchjs/nightwatch/wiki/Page-Object-API).

To be honest I am not all that familiar with Nightwatch. I can look at any additions to your PR and take your word for it. If you'd like to become a maintainer of this definition I will approve that as well.
I have no intention of becoming maintainer of this definition, but I will gladly revise this PR to more accurately reflect the actual JS interface.
